project_details: Kenko is a health tracking app designed to help users monitor their daily activities, meals, sleep, and overall health trends. The app provides detailed insights into users' health progress and suggests improvements for better wellness.

Urban Explorer is an interactive app for city dwellers looking to discover hidden gems in their local area. It offers detailed reviews, ratings, and GPS-based maps to help people explore new places in their cities.

EcoMove is a sustainable transport app that provides users with eco-friendly transportation options like bicycles, electric scooters, and carpooling. It aims to reduce carbon footprints by encouraging greener alternatives to cars.

CookMaster is a recipe-sharing platform that helps users find and share cooking recipes, track ingredients, and create grocery shopping lists. The app offers personalized meal suggestions based on dietary preferences and available ingredients.
